<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5300237011929698192">William Landay is the author of the <i>New York Times</i> bestseller <i>Defending Jacob</i>. Previous novels include <i>Mission Flats</i>, winner of the Dagger Award for best debut crime novel, and <i>The Strangler</i>, which was an <i>L.A. Times</i> favorite crime novel and nominated for the <i>Strand Magazine</i> Critics Award as best crime novel of the year.</span>

